  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Zoo-tto Mahjong! is a Nintendo developed and published Super Famicom video game. It was released on July 1, 1998. It is a simple game of Mahjong, of which there were many that were created by Nintendo. It was the last Mahjong game developed for the Super Famicom, and a preview version was also available through Satellaview. In the game you choose which animal you want to play as before the game starts.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
